Author: dfranke
Content: Keep in mind, though, that at least part of the reason that some places have a higher cost-of-living is that it's more desirable to live there.  I'd certainly rather live in Boston than Houston.

Author: jcwentz
Content: Sounds like a bad plan to make privacy a contractual obligation, because then you're undertaking a legal obligation not to have your server hacked.  No one who understands servers would do that.
